                    <h4>How long has InMotion Hosting been in business?</h4>
                    <p>InMotion Hosting has been hosting shared accounts since our inception in 2001.</p>
                    <p>InMotion Hosting, Inc. is registered in the State of California, USA.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="g_why" id="g_why"></a>
                <h4>Why should I choose InMotion Hosting?</h4>
                    <p>Service</p>
                    <p>InMotion Hosting has been voted #1 for our superior customer and technical service by many independent reviewers. Our 'service first' philosophy has allowed us to be one of the strongest and most reliable web hosting forces on the internet, building a client base of happy eBusiness and personal web hosting clients.</p>
                    <p>Stability</p>
                    <p>We provide a world class infrastructure and a top notch network so you can avoid costly investments in hardware, software, and system administration. We have a first rate BGP4 Network with state of the art fault tolerant IP routing to ensure your website stays up.</p>
                    <p>Growth Potential</p>
                    <p>InMotion Hosting offers <a href="/business-hosting">three shared hosting plans</a> along with <a href="/vps-hosting">VPS</a> and <a href="/dedicated-servers">V-Dedicated</a> plans, all with increasing levels of functionality, allowing you stay ahead of the competition as your business grows.</p>
                    <p>We are a reliable and affordable web hosting company with years of experience. We operate our own servers over which we have full control. We have a team of system administrators who are monitoring our servers 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="g_moneyback" id="g_moneyback"></a>
                <h4>Do you offer a Money Back guarantee?</h4>
                    <p>Yes!</p>
                    <p> We offer a 30-day money back guarantee on Value Class packages and a 90-day* money back guarantee on Business Class packages. If you are not satisfied with our service in any way, we will refund all hosting charges, no questions asked.</p>
                    <p> There is no refund for domain names, as you are given full ownership of the domain name for the year. You may transfer your domain name away at that time. There are no refunds upon completion of the 30th day of hosting with InMotion. *Monthly contracts have a one month money back guarantee. <a href="/30day">Read more</a>.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="g_hiddencharges" id="g_hiddencharges"></a>
                <h4>Are there any hidden charges?</h4>
                    <p>No. We will not charge you for anything without your prior consent.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="p_howlong" id="p_howlong"></a>
                <h4>How long will it take to set up my account?</h4>
                    <p>Your account will be activated the very same business day.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top2">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="p_payment" id="p_payment"></a>
                <h4>What forms of payment do you accept?</h4>
                    <p>We accept Visa, MasterCard, American Express and Discover.</p>
                    <p>Payments by check or money order must be mailed to our mailing address. Make checks payable to InMotion Hosting, Inc.</p>
                    <p>We do not accept cash.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top2">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="p_upgrade" id="p_upgrade"></a>
                <h4>Can I upgrade my hosting plan at a later stage?</h4>
                    <p>Yes.</p>
                    <p>All accounts can be upgraded. Upgrades will happen the same business day.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top2">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="p_upgradefee" id="p_upgradefee"></a>
                <h4>When I upgrade, do I have to pay a setup fee again?</h4>
                    <p>No. Setup fees (which are waived on all year long sign-ups) are one time fees.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top2">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="p_invoice" id="p_invoice"></a>
                <h4>How will you invoice me?</h4>
                    <p>All accounts renew automatically. For customers paying by check or who request notice before billing, invoices are sent via email.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top2">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="p_popup" id="p_popup"></a>
                <h4>Do you put banners or pop-ups on my web pages?</h4>
                    <p>No. We never change or tamper with your website.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top2">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="p_techsupport" id="p_techsupport"></a>
