                <a name="t_servers" id="t_servers"></a>
                <h4>What kind of servers do you use?</h4>
                    <p>All of our servers are 100% Dell PowerEdge servers with CentOS operating systems. Depending on the primary function, the machines will have from 2GB to 48GB RAM, 2 to 16 processors, and 2-24 hard drives.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top3">return to top</a></p>
