                    <p><a href="#top3">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="t_mysql" id="t_mysql"></a>
                <h4>What version of MySQL do you use?</h4>
                    <p>We currently run MySQL 5.x by default, but we have servers that run 4.0.x and 4.1.x available by request for those needing older versions.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top3">return to top</a></p>

