                    <p><a href="#top3">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="d_domain" id="d_domain"></a>
                <h4>Can I purchase a domain name with InMotion Hosting?</h4>
                    <p>Yes.</p>
                    <p> You can order .com,.net,.org,.biz and .info domain names for $11.95, at the time of signup. You get full ownership of the domain name for 1 year.<a href="/domains"> Learn more about domain names here</a></p>
                    <p>If you want to purchase a domain name with a different extension, we suggest you purchase it from a 3rd party program, and set your nameservers to:</p>
                    <p>NS.INMOTIONHOSTING.COM - ip 74.124.210.242<br />
                     NS2.INMOTIONHOSTING.COM - ip 66.117.7.112</p>
                    <p>Then, at the time of sign up, choose 'I own this domain' and continue the order process.</p>
                    <p><a href="#top4">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="d_nohost" id="d_nohost"></a>
                <h4>Can I purchase a domain name without purchasing a hosting account?</h4>
                   <p>Yes, you can . You can purchase .com,.net, .org, .biz, .us and .info domain names for $11.95 a year. Click <a href="/domains">here</a> and enter the domain you would like to purchase,  it is available, you can purchase it without hosting.</p>
                <a name="d_point" id="d_point"></a>
                <h4>I already have a domain name. How do I point it to my new account?</h4>
                    <p>In order to point your domain at our servers, you should contact (via phone or their website) the company who sold you the domain and ask them to modify the nameservers to reflect the following information:</p>
                    <p>NS.INMOTIONHOSTING.COM - ip 74.124.210.242<br />
                     NS2.INMOTIONHOSTING.COM - ip 66.117.7.112</p>
                    <p><a href="#top4">return to top</a></p>
                <a name="d_pointwhy" id="d_pointwhy"></a>
                <h4>I've changed my domain name servers over, and my website is not coming up. How come?</h4>
                    <p>Once you have changed the nameservers for your domain name, it takes anywhere from 24-72 hours for your domain name to fully propagate over to our servers. However, in the mean time, you can access your website via a temporary url. (http://servername.inmotionhosting.com/~username)</p>
                    <p>If you experience any other problems with your domain, please contact <a href="/contact">support</a>.</p>
